    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-parked and sparkling clean. It's been super reliable and drives like a cloud. I'm really looking for a smooth, easy hand-off to someone who will love it as much as I do, so I've priced it to sell quickly! Feel free to reach out with any questions! \u2728",
