    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a factory Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen is mechanically flawless, having received documented preventative subframe reinforcement, a complete VANOS overhaul, and rod bearing replacement. The chassis remains taut with OEM bushings and factory-spec dampers, while the limited-slip differential provides surgical power delivery. The exterior retains its original deep luster, free of rock chips or swirling, complemented by an interior with zero bolster wear or pixel degradation. This is an analog masterpiece for the serious collector, offering a linear 8,000 RPM powerband and a pure, unadulterated connection to the road.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
