      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior features a flawless factory finish with no chips, swirls, or imperfections, while the interior still retains that new-car scent, with premium leather surfaces that show zero wear. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with full documentation included. Always garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather, this car drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. If you are looking for an investment-grade example that requires absolutely nothing but a new home, this is it.",
